data.description: THE SELLER IS WILLING TO CONTRIBUTE UP TO $5000 at closing for the buyer to use for closing costs, rate buy down, or other expenses. Stunning Gem in Bridgeford Crossing – Where Elegance Meets Convenience! Step into a haven of contemporary design, nestled within the sought-after gated community of Bridgeford Crossing. This 4 BD/ 2 BA beauty exudes a harmonious blend of sophistication and warmth. Prepare culinary delights in a kitchen tailor-made for the modern chef: granite countertops, sleek stainless-steel appliances, and a magnificent island that doubles as a breakfast bar. Adjacent, the dining space seamlessly transitions to the expansive living area, ensuring entertaining or family time is always an intimate affair. Find tranquility in the private master suite, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and a lavish en suite bathroom. Delight in the dual granite-topped sink vanity and an oversized walk-in shower. The home’s split design ensures the additional bedrooms enjoy a quiet retreat, with effortless access to the well-appointed main bathroom. But the allure doesn't end indoors. Revel in serene outdoor moments on your oversized screened lanai, overlooking a calming lake – nature’s melody providing the perfect backdrop. Bridgeford Crossing isn’t just a place to live – it’s a lifestyle. Delight in a suite of amenities, from the bustling clubhouse, complete with game tables, kitchen bar-top seating, a fitness room, heated pool, and even a movie theater. Revel in games of tennis, engage in friendly community gatherings, or simply bask by the pool. With internet service, lawn care, and even basic cable covered, life here is as effortless as it is luxurious. Convenience is key with easy access to US Hwy. 27, downtown Davenport's shopping district, and the I-4. Experience the magic with Disney less than 30 minutes away or take on the bustling vibe of Downtown Orlando, just 35 minutes away. Discover your dream home. Discover Bridgeford Crossing. Don't miss out - Book your exclusive showing today!
